# Proposal Writer — AgriPro (re-run: fix final-ceo defect)

## Fix Applied

final-ceo.out identified ONE blocking defect: all 4 proposal/media PNGs were
byte-for-byte identical (MD5 593076e2…, 15 KB each), making the one-pager and
deck embed the same blank frame three times.

**Fix executed:**
1. Served `michaelwegter.com/public/` on localhost:7777 (public root, not demo folder,
   so absolute asset paths `/demos/agripro/assets/...` resolve correctly).
2. Recaptured 3 DISTINCT real frames with Playwright (recapture.mjs):
   - `hero.png`   → Procurement role, Inspections table loaded   — 131 KB, MD5 1532d8f9
   - `step-1.png` → Quality/Lab role, Documents/OCR panel        — 111 KB, MD5 1bca19ab
   - `step-2.png` → Quality/Lab role, flagged inspection detail   — 165 KB, MD5 14a0aaab
   All 3 MD5s are distinct; all well above 100 KB. No duplicates.
3. Re-ran `build-deck.py` → deck.pptx rebuilt at 420 KB (was 41 KB), confirming
   all three real screenshots are now embedded.
4. one-pager.html embeds the same media/ files by relative path — no rebuild needed,
   it now renders distinct real frames.
5. cover-letter.md and one-pager.html: dash scan (U+2014/U+2013/entities) → CLEAN.

